      "value": "<p><em><strong>Spiritual Peace.</strong></em> The krevaaki are a species at one with the world around them, able to refocus negative emotions and end confrontations peacefully as they progress through life. When you reach 5th level, you learn and can cast the calm emotions force power once per day, targeting yourself. Wisdom is your forcecasting ability for this power.</p>",
